## id: teltonika-login
## name: Teltonika Login Panel - Detect
## author: hack007x
## severity: info
## tags: panel,teltonika,edb,discovery
## description: Teltonika login panel was detected.
## affects: rut900
## reference: https://www.exploit-db.com/ghdb/7819
